        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Ending Payments to Non-American Citizens Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits making amounts from the Judgment Fund available to an alien who is not a lawful permanent resident unless specifically authorized by law. (The Judgment Fund is an account for paying judgments and settlements against the United States.)</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
